snippet.title: Dolly - Official Trailer (2026) Fabianne Therese, Seann William Scott, and Max the Impaler.
snippet.description:
Check out the Dolly trailer for this upcoming horror movie starring Fabianne Therese, Seann William Scott, Ethan Suplee, and Max the Impaler.

A young woman, Macy, fights for survival after being abducted by a deranged, monster-like figure who wants to raise Macy as their child. A daring blend of New French Extremity and 1970s American horror.

Dolly is written by Rod Blackhurst and Brandon Weavil. It is directed by Rod Blackhurst.

Dolly opens in theaters on March 6, 2026.
